data.description: Large corner lot with beautiful landscape and solar. The luxury Silverstone ranch living is the place you’ve been looking for. The floor plan is a nice open space that gives natural light and volume ceilings. Gourmet kitchen opens up to the family area With a eat in nook area, breakfast bar, beautiful countertops and plenty of cabinet space for storage. The master room features a beautiful bay window that is separate from the other rooms.  You’re beautiful master bathroom has dual sinks, garden bathtub, with a separate shower in your master bath. High ceilings with an oversized two car garage that also has electric car hook up. Beautiful large size backyard that is Easy to maintain, low maintenance with nice landscaping. This home has access to walking trails that are just a short distance from the property. Also quite close to tule Springs Park, Floyd Lamb Park, shopping, restaurants and freeways. You’ll definitely want to check this property out.  $5000 towards closing by seller!
